<p>
  Thanks for signing up to <strong><%= site_name %></strong>,
  <%= name.first %>!
</p>

<p>
  To continue creating your <%= site_name %> account,
  click the link below.
</p>

<%= helpers.button[verify_url, "Verify your account"] %>

<p>
  If the above link does not work, copy and paste the following link into your
  browser:

  <a href="<%= verify_url %>"><%= verify_url %></a>
</p>

<p>
  This verification link will expire in 3 days
  <%= token_expiry.strftime("(on %Y-%m-%d at %H:%M %Z)") %>,
  after which you will have to fill out the <%= site_name %>
  sign up form again if you wish to continue your signup.
</p>

<p>
  If you did not request to sign up to <%= site_name %>, you can safely
  ignore this email.
</p>

<p>
  Have a great day!
</p>
